Which region has the largest market share in the hearing aid fitting software market?
The North America region currently holds the largest market share in the hearing aid fitting software market, followed by Europe and Asia Pacific.

What are the major challenges faced by the hearing aid fitting software market?
The high cost of hearing aid devices, limited reimbursement for hearing aid fittings, and lack of awareness among the elderly population are the major challenges faced by the market.

What are the emerging trends in the hearing aid fitting software market?
Integration of artificial intelligence in hearing aid fitting software, development of smartphone-compatible hearing aid apps, and increasing adoption of teleaudiology services are the emerging trends in the market.

